You raise your magnum to ready strike and then swing downwards as fast as you can. However, the swordsman was able to sidestep the attack at the last second and countered with a quick stab to the chest. Maybe next time you get into a fight, you should just focus on winning and not trying to look cool.\n\nGame Over\n\n[[Restart from last Checkpoint|ambush]]\n\n[img[stabbedagain]]

How lovely! You get teleported to a beach with really nice scenery. As you stand still admiring the view, you start to fell a little bit warm...\n\n[[Continue|Burned]]\n\n[img[beach]]
As you open the door at the end of the dark hallway, you see a some light coming out, who knows what will await you behind this door. You are about to find out...\n\n[[Continue|ambush]]\n\n[img[door3]]
Unfortunately, being a shut-in makes you extremely vulnerable to even small exposures of direct sunlight. As a result, you catch on fire and turn into a small pile of ashes.\n\nGame Over\n\n[[Restart from Last Checkpoint|Adventure]]\n\n[img[fire]]
You quickly throw your arms up in front of you to intercept the blow. Unfortunately, fleshy, unprotected human arms don't stop cold bladed steel very well. As a result the sword goes right through your arms into your chest where you lie on the floor and slowly bleed out.\n\nGame Over\n\n[[Restart from last Checkpoint?|ambush]]\n\n[img[stabbed]]
"Screw it, i'll just take the sword." you thought to yourself.\n\nAfter posing heroically with it, you place it in your inventory and head to the door.\n\n[[Continue|nextdoor]]\n\n
As you walk inside the room the door abruptly closes behind you leaving you in a dimly lit room. Suddenly, the air fills with smoke and a strong scent of gunpowder. As the smoke clears, a light in the middle of the room showcases a smug figure sitting on what appears to be a throne chair made out of guns.\n\n"HUMAN, I am the King of Guns and I have the very key that you seek. However, you must defeat me before you can have it back. I am impressed you were able to defeat my personal bodyguard but, you only won because he likes to use swords. Prepare youself for battle mortal!" bellowed the King of Guns.\n\nWill you be able to defeat the evil king and get your keys? Or will your jouney end as a bullet-riddled corpse. You approach your door bedroom door and get ready to start your quest. However, breakfast is the most important meal of the day. Before going you snack on a //Snickers// bar to give you enough energy to get through the day.\n\nAs you leave your room you find yourself walking a down a very strange set of stairs that you've never seen before. This is all very creepy since your supposed to be the only one home. At the bottom of the staircase you stop at two doors and decide whether to go through [[door #1|door1]] or [[door #2|door2]].
You head over the door and get ready to open it. It has been a long and perilous journey but you must press on for spring break is the perfect time to get to rank 1 at Heroes of the Storm.\n\n[[Continue|The End?]]\n\n[img[door3]]
The Quest for Gaming\n
The initial warm lighting is quickly replaced by total darkness and a long corridor. The only illumination coming in the form of a dim light underneath what you believe is a door. After a short, but intense battle you come out victorious. As you take a moment to rest you noticed the swordsman dropped his sword on the ground. \n\n"That's a pretty nice sword, would be a waste to just leave it there. Then again, guns are better anyway," you thought to yourself.\n\nYou search the entire room but, couldn't find your computer room keys. All hope seemed to be lost until you see another door in this room. \n\nWill you [[continue to the door|nextdoor]] or will you [[pick up the sword first|pickup]]?\n\n[img[dead]]

It's finally spring break and that means no more classes and homework for the one whole week. After doing nothing but studying for midterms, finishing up projects, and writing essays; You feel as though you deserved this break. Finally you get to do nothing but sleep in, watch anime, and play video games.\n\nAfter sleeping in until noon, you summon the strength to sit up out of your comfortable-ass bed. As you collect your thoughts, you finally decided to [[go play Heroes of the Storm with your homies|Check keys]].\n\n[img[bedroom]]

Just as soon as you walk past the door, a dark hooded figure wielding a sword jumps out behind a corner and is about to stab you. You only have seconds to react before you die a painful, bloody death.\n\nYou can attempt to [[Block|blocked]] or [[Parry|parried]] the attack.\n\n[img[attack]]
Almost immediately however, the swordsman quickly steps back and readies himself for a powerful lunge attack. While he is charging up his attack you decided to [[finish him off with a stylish pistol whip|pistol whip]] or a [[boring but practical headshot|HEADSHOT]].\n\n[img[readyup]]
You slowly crack open the first door. As you open it wave of light flows through its cracks. Perhaps this door will lead you to your keys.\n\n[[Continue|Behind Door 1]]\n\n[img[opensesame]]
